window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Being a dragon is awesome, but even dragons dream of simpler things. </p> <p>Leo’s blossoming empire is a safe haven where humans and beastkin work side by side. He spends his days tending the village, helping the sweet foxgirl forage, sparring with the beautiful high elf, and keeping the impish witch out of trouble.<br> <br> But peace is hard to hold onto, even for a dragon. As a scheming coven closes in, Leo must rally his allies. Dragon’s Lake teeters on the brink of destruction or greatness.<br> <br> Will a dragon’s strength be enough to protect them all?</p>"; 
